title: Cable Ready, Carpeting, Dishwasher, On-Site Maintenance
posting_body: ['Welcome to Greenway Apartments!', 'Welcome to Greenway Apartments in Minneapolis, Minnesota!', 'Greenway offers studio, one bedroom and two bedroom units in a cozy and private multi building setting.', 'Conveniently located just a short stroll away from the Midtown Greenway and Eat Street with easy access to shopping, dining, and biking trails.', 'Enjoy the great outdoors by going for a ride on the 5 mile long Midtown Greenway trail.', 'Savor the variety of cuisines that Eat Street has to offer by visiting the collection of tremendous affordable eateries running North to South from downtown Minneapolis along Nicollet Ave.', 'Call today to schedule your personal tour!', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 750 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Gas Range', '- Dishwasher', '- Carpeting', '- Refrigerator', '- Disposal', '- Cable Ready', 'Community Amenities', '- On-Site Management', '- Laundry Facilities', '- On-Site Maintenance', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats Allowed With Pet Fee at Move In', 'Income Requirements:', '2.5 times the Rent', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Greenway Apartments', '2736 Blaisdell Ave South, Minneapolis, MN, 55408', 'uUWtm3TW']
